<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- rajāʾu qal̊bī rạsikẖuⁿ ạ̉sāsuhu birũ ạlmasīḥ̊
 walaẙsa sẖayʾuⁿ gẖaẙruhu qal̊by ạ̹laẙhi yas̊taryiḥ̊

[C1]
   ạlqrạr: ʿalaẙka yạ ṣakẖ̊ra ạlạ̉zal̊
   (ạủl̊qī rajạỷy wālạ̉mal̊)2

[V2]
 2- lan̊ taḥjuba ạlẓũl̊mātu ʿan̊ ʿaẙny muḥaỹạhu ạlṣãbīḥ̊
 faniʿ̊maẗu ạlrãbĩ ạlʿalī taj̊lū līa ạlḥaqã ạlṣãrīḥ

[V3]
 3- fī ʿah̊dihi ạlmkẖ̊tūmi bạ ldãmi ạltẖãmīni lī ạlrãjā
 ạ̹n taʿ̊ṣifi ạlạ̉n̊wạʾu ḥw lī lạ ạ̉kẖāfu ạllũjajā

[V4]
 4- waḥīna yā̉tī ạlrãbũ fy ạl̊ ạ̉m̊jạdi fy ạlyaẘmi ạlạ̉kẖīr̊
 ạảb̊dūa ladayhi ṭāhirạa bitẖaẘbi birĩhi ạlmunīr̊</lyrics>
<title>rjạʾ qlby rạskẖ</title>
<author>brạdywry wlym, mlḥm dẖhbyẗ</author>
<hymn_number>8476</hymn_number>
</song>